{"tid":639784,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：廠迷分歧令我離隊","createTime":"2018-04-23T18:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T18:24:51.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36c0045c4985bc5d6bf0bb05ab2f48efff41e6cb","tid":639784,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2gI2XDl7WEhrXNf%2Bo0l6DAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fe5c045a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加首次回應出廠，表示全球廠迷就著其去留問題出現分歧，導致球會形象受損，是他決定離隊的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n雲加（Arsene Wenger）於上周六發表出廠宣言後，周一出席記者會，席間當然被追問離隊的話題。對於出廠其中原因，雲加暗示自己得不到廠迷一致的擁護：「我相信球會在全世界都受到尊重，但粉絲的形象欠團結，這不是我希望見到的，令人感到受傷害。」<br />\n<br />\n該名法籍教頭補充：「對我來說，這家球會的超卓形象非常重要，而體育並非只是贏輸。我擔憂球會的國際形象受損，我不是生球迷的氣，如果球會能夠像我希望的發展下去，這較我的留低更加重要。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，雲加坦言未來執教另一支英超球隊的機會極微，他謂：「假如談到情感，領導另一支球隊對壘阿仙奴，情感上我會感到非常困難。雖然不能肯定不會接掌英超球會，但這刻我是屬於這家球會（阿仙奴）。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/3/293/21173571293/21185228003_600x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F3%2F293%2F21173571293%2F21185228003_600x389.jpg&h=0a23fe6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c660475eaaa5a103188d6d9bdd36e802f18dd5c5","tid":639784,"uid":4957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:10:54.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母暴龍哥"},{"pid":"31a64806754c114a6e5707bbc313d2de3f55a6d4","tid":639784,"uid":128100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"迷雲同反雲黨既分歧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e527bc8a56148d87704591dead37066d64a6f19","tid":639784,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"反雲又然"},{"pid":"8fde65585b637e9b7d8fe4320bf87f82fe66b99e","tid":639784,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235200a03b50cbc575d9f4187d92cf92dd0e9c5d","tid":639784,"uid":119064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"雲加犧牲自己黎團結球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}